{"tid":2428782,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"第一屆第二季賽馬真飛博擊王","createTime":"2021-03-01T20:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T15:03:20.000Z","uid":254675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6c60dacd4f048dc270325d8cffe7183d0f8876d6","tid":2428782,"uid":254675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T20:33:05.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"violet\">切勿沉迷賭博 賭錢落海</span></span><br />\n［本比賽純屬娛樂性質］<br />\n第二個季度為 3/3/2021至28/04/2021 (17次賽事）<br />\n第二個季度報名可在<span class=\"x-large\"> 3/3/2021</span>晚上6時後報名，可以搶先打「<strong>報名</strong>」或<strong>出真飛</strong>預留是季參賽席位<br />\n-----我是分界線-----<br />\n<br />\n參賽規則<br />\n1.每個賽馬日投注最多<span class=\"red\">$500</span><br />\n2.另設不投注選項（仍可提供心水，不計入積分）<br />\n3.比賽真飛<span class=\"red\">只需要在開跑前貼上</span>投注紀錄，開跑後不受理。<br />\n4.每人底分為2500分，最高積分則為該季<span class=\"gold\">真飛博撃王</span>！<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>第一季真飛博擊王冠軍</strong></span>－<span class=\"gold\">Regen</span> (+3305) <br />\n5.派彩每$1為1分<br />\n6.參加者需年滿18歲<br />\n7.每季首五名可以獲得下一個季度優先出賽權<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>第一季首五名</strong></span><br />\nRegen<br />\n雲比沙卡雲尼<br />\n大袋鼠<br />\n門關起的一刻<br />\n幸運快車"},{"pid":"e27b3cdbbd8c85fb6ad782e2612a192b2879e74b","tid":2428782,"uid":254675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T20:33:54.000Z","msg":"賽馬-第一屆真飛博撃王(1)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2320410\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2320410</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2b5d43e151994800e3f3953f908758d007d1aac8","tid":2428782,"uid":254675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jnh1XpH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJnh1XpH.png&h=281a1559&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"388fb043f77c1084de5bbf096174e7a76d9d4a2d","tid":2428782,"uid":254675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:50:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oc31dEW